    <div class="calc-layout">
      <div class="calc-main">
        <h1>⏱️ Hours Calculator</h1>
        <p class="calc-intro">Add or subtract hours and minutes, calculate hours worked and find the time difference between two times.</p>

        <div class="card">
          <label>Mode</label>
          <select id="hrs-modo" onchange="toggleHours()">
            <option value="sumar">Add durations</option>
            <option value="restar">Subtract durations</option>
            <option value="diferencia">Time difference (start → end)</option>
          </select>

          <div id="hrs-duraciones">
            <div class="row-2">
              <div><label>Hours (1)</label><input type="number" id="hrs-h1" placeholder="3" oninput="calcHours()"></div>
              <div><label>Minutes (1)</label><input type="number" id="hrs-m1" placeholder="45" oninput="calcHours()"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="row-2">
              <div><label>Hours (2)</label><input type="number" id="hrs-h2" placeholder="1" oninput="calcHours()"></div>
              <div><label>Minutes (2)</label><input type="number" id="hrs-m2" placeholder="30" oninput="calcHours()"></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div id="hrs-horas" style="display:none">
            <div class="row-2">
              <div>
                <label>Start time</label>
                <input type="time" id="hrs-ini" oninput="calcHours()" style="width:100%;padding:0.65rem 0.9rem;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;font-size:1rem;background:var(--bg);margin-bottom:1rem">
              </div>
              <div>
                <label>End time</label>
                <input type="time" id="hrs-fin" oninput="calcHours()" style="width:100%;padding:0.65rem 0.9rem;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;font-size:1rem;background:var(--bg);margin-bottom:1rem">
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="result-box" id="hrs-res">Enter the times</div>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-top:2rem;padding-top:1.5rem;border-top:1px solid var(--border)">
          <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:1rem">How to add hours and minutes</h2>
          <p style="color:var(--muted);font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.8">Adding hours and minutes is trickier than adding regular numbers because the system is base-60 — 90 minutes equals 1 hour 30 minutes, not 1 hour 90 minutes. This calculator handles the conversion automatically. For example, 3h 45min + 1h 30min = 5h 15min (because 45 + 30 = 75 minutes = 1 hour 15 minutes).</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <aside class="calc-sidebar">
